version_description:
- 3D动作点触摸的支持
- 保存在导入/导出日期
- 错误修正

- Emergency Login with Touch ID
- No more crash while browsing your photos

- Finally you can bypass passcode with touch ID!
- New all in one camera with live photo support

- gif，实时照片和视频之间的互换
- 支持视频编辑 - 修剪，裁剪，反转和慢动作

- 通过WiFi导入和导出照片
- 性能改进- 通过WiFi导入和导出照片
- 性能改进
- 修正了一些小错误
- 修正了一些小错误

- 支持iOS 11的HEIC映像文件
- 通过iTunes文件共享增强备份和还原
- Bug修复
- Support for iOS11 and new iPhone devices

- Supports iCloud backup and restore
- Supports option to delete unnecessary caches and reclaim storage space
- Support for iOS 13
- Support for Dark mode
- Support for new iPhone devices
- Misc. UI enhancements
- Minor bug fixes

- Now you can optionally bypass pattern lock by bio authentication.
- Fixed a bug of iCloud backup failure.
